{"tid":2342393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鳥籠底鬆脫鴿子飛上樹 女主人向消防求助","createTime":"2020-12-27T05:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T08:09:12.000Z","uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e62271befffdd891762725e90edffc80825ee2","tid":2342393,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:53:51.000Z","msg":"一名吳姓女子昨午（25日）到西貢，準備將飼養的鴿子交給友人託管，其間鳥籠底部鬆脫，鴿子飛到樹上，吳女報警求助。消防昨午至今晨（26日）三度到場協助，惟未能救回鴿子。吳女稱，愛護動物協會人員到場後，稱鴿子應在樹上，故未有協助救回。愛協回覆查詢表示，該鴿子疑為散養家禽，活動能力正常，沒有受傷或被困，加上接近該鴿子有相當難度，遂建議暫緩採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201226/s00001/1608953202643/%e9%b3%a5%e7%b1%a0%e5%ba%95%e9%ac%86%e8%84%ab%e9%b4%bf%e5%ad%90%e9%a3%9b%e4%b8%8a%e6%a8%b9%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e5%a0%b1%e8%ad%a6-%e6%b6%88%e9%98%b2%e4%b8%89%e6%8f%b4%e7%84%a1%e6%9e%9c-%e6%84%9b%e5%8d%94-%e7%84%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%82%b7%e9%9b%a3%e6%8e%a5%e8%bf%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%ad%b0%e6%9a%ab%e7%b7%a9%e8%a1%8c%e5%8b%95\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201226%2Fs00001%2F1608953202643%2F%25e9%25b3%25a5%25e7%25b1%25a0%25e5%25ba%2595%25e9%25ac%2586%25e8%2584%25ab%25e9%25b4%25bf%25e5%25ad%2590%25e9%25a3%259b%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%25a8%25b9%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e8%25ad%25a6-%25e6%25b6%2588%25e9%2598%25b2%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%258f%25b4%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%259e%259c-%25e6%2584%259b%25e5%258d%2594-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7%25e9%259b%25a3%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25bf%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259a%25ab%25e7%25b7%25a9%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%258b%2595&d=sZqGLlkYYIxatccyfr7NWLktNrE0CDS5yYjP391fFHI%3D&h=da83c9fd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20201226%2Fs00001%2F1608953202643%2F%25e9%25b3%25a5%25e7%25b1%25a0%25e5%25ba%2595%25e9%25ac%2586%25e8%2584%25ab%25e9%25b4%25bf%25e5%25ad%2590%25e9%25a3%259b%25e4%25b8%258a%25e6%25a8%25b9%25e4%25b8%25bb%25e4%25ba%25ba%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e8%25ad%25a6-%25e6%25b6%2588%25e9%2598%25b2%25e4%25b8%2589%25e6%258f%25b4%25e7%2584%25a1%25e6%259e%259c-%25e6%2584%259b%25e5%258d%2594-%25e7%2584%25a1%25e5%258f%2597%25e5%2582%25b7%25e9%259b%25a3%25e6%258e%25a5%25e8%25bf%2591%25e5%25bb%25ba%25e8%25ad%25b0%25e6%259a%25ab%25e7%25b7%25a9%25e8%25a1%258c%25e5%258b%2595&h=d9209c5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20201226/s00001/1608953202643/%e9%b3%a5%e7%b1%a0%e5%ba%95%e9%ac%86%e8%84%ab%e9%b4%bf%e5%ad%90%e9%a3%9b%e4%b8%8a%e6%a8%b9%e4%b8%bb%e4%ba%ba%e5%a0%b1%e8%ad%a6-%e6%b6%88%e9%98%b2%e4%b8%89%e6%8f%b4%e7%84%a1%e6%9e%9c-%e6%84%9b%e5%8d%94-%e7%84%a1%e5%8f%97%e5%82%b7%e9%9b%a3%e6%8e%a5%e8%bf%91%e5%bb%ba%e8%ad%b0%e6%9a%ab%e7%b7%a9%e8%a1%8c%e5%8b%95</a><br />\n<br />\n吳小姐說，約7個月前於街上發現「春春」，當時牠疑從鳥巢墮下受傷，由於未能找到鳥巢，她遂將「春春」帶回家治理。吳小姐認為，「春春」自幼被飼養，未必能適應野外生活。"},{"pid":"c0b88a39ab3d87f0b53c497eb52a158e38d99acc","tid":2342393,"uid":36494,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:54:41.000Z","msg":"愛協回覆表示，該鴿子疑為散養家禽，人員在場觀察，認為該鴿子活動能力正常，能自如地在樹上飛來飛去，沒有受傷或被困，未見有任何即時危險。愛協稱，當時鴿子在約3層樓高位置，要接近該鴿有相當難度，遂建議暫緩採取行動。愛協續指出，動物督察服務為義務服務，需按個案急切性進行評估，優先處理緊急、有動物身處險境的個案。<br />\n<br />\n愛協又引述《公眾衛生（動物及禽鳥）（禽畜飼養的發牌）規例》及《廢物處置條例》指出，市民如未獲得漁護署發出特別牌照而散養任何活家禽如雞、鴨、鵝、鴿和鵪鶉均屬違法。"},{"pid":"0f3c52e7a57595a9d0cea6a37e69f391e252c082","tid":2342393,"uid":39383,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"咁小事都call 消防, 肚餓自然識落地架啦, 拎d 野食出黎咪得囉"},{"pid":"cd1477823b3b13965728172e635c75502fe06767","tid":2342393,"uid":42426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"吳小姐失去青春了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30ec7c38408fcc652cbab539a71e4314e1f8fb8b","tid":2342393,"uid":89869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:58:26.000Z","msg":"係唔係想攞去俾人煲綠豆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6a9a71903003ea936fab97b4eda33244904828b","tid":2342393,"uid":56511,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"cd1477823b3b13965728172e635c75502fe06767","tid":2342393,"uid":42426,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T05:57:37.000Z","msg":"吳小姐失去青春了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail2_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:13:38.000Z","msg":"係春春..."},{"pid":"4d00dfacf37356c6bb396d55940a13c12a50bae3","tid":2342393,"uid":221650,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:15:08.000Z","msg":"睇錯底褲鬆脫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66e17e2033ba460f83f31df46e2dc7a9a5d7815","tid":2342393,"uid":171786,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:32:31.000Z","msg":"個女主人都on撚9，浪費人力物力"},{"pid":"552b8f32efddccf73c53b9a32203454431578847","tid":2342393,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"吳小姐 = 中共<br />\n白鴿 = 香港"},{"pid":"45da37006aca3b9af521d7a4eb33230fe8ea0493","tid":2342393,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T07:27:57.000Z","msg":"好心就順便放生"},{"pid":"13657fb549b09b5cb63e065f95cb92155da57208","tid":2342393,"uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"叫飛行服務隊黎幫手嘛，反正班撚樣都無野做。<br />\n揸架直升機黎救咪救到"},{"pid":"b90aa87903694fe70772de50d5c3a09a2581716f","tid":2342393,"uid":7323,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"13657fb549b09b5cb63e065f95cb92155da57208","tid":2342393,"uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:03:20.000Z","msg":"叫飛行服務隊黎幫手嘛，反正班撚樣都無野做。<br />\n揸架直升機黎救咪救到"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">同意啊，平時都無野做架啦。</span>"},{"pid":"2f02983f0f4e892e97dc6cfb34bda7619602e869","tid":2342393,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"552b8f32efddccf73c53b9a32203454431578847","tid":2342393,"uid":215755,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T06:38:08.000Z","msg":"吳小姐 = 中共<br />\n白鴿 = 香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T08:09:12.000Z","msg":"吳小姐 = 民主黨死忠<br />\n白　鴿 = 見勢色不對「總辭」潛水 / 走佬既 民主黨七子"}]}